This Project includes tow stepper motors, LCD desplay and an arduino.
-buttons
-basic resisters
-basic capacitors
schematic attached to repository

a sideways movement combined with pan creates a wide angle observation of a object that can either be,
recorded real-time or timelapsed.

this design is also modular meaning the rails of the slider can be extended to any desired lenght.

